title: SF001 - SF339 Sunfly Hits Karaoke Complete
description:
I hope this torrent is not too ambitious (having all the 339 Sunfly Hits collection in a single torrent).

I have been collecting Sunfly Hits Karaoke since 2007, so I'm sharing to you now all the Sunfly Hits Karaoke collection from the first 1 until the latest 339th release (as of May 25th 2014).

I will be seeding this for quite a while (I have a seeding box that is switched on 24/7), so everybody, please seed for quite a while too.

Enjoy!!
